// Multi-hop variant of `unknown_method.relon`: the path-walker
// resolves the prefix `o.customer` to `Schema("User")`, but `User`
// has no method named `wave`. Same `UnknownMethod` we emit for the
// 2-segment form should fire here.
#schema User {
    String name: *
} with {
    greet() -> String: f"hello ${self.name}"
}

#schema Order {
    User customer: *
}

#main(Order o)
{ String s: o.customer.wave() }
